column14: Dr Gene RTZ-113 Weighing Scale: Flipkart.com
column17:
Dr Gene RTZ-113 Weighing Scale Price: Rs.825

Features : Analog Display Non Slip Platform Max Load 120 Kgs Extra Large Display 1 Kg graduation 1 Year Warranty. Specifications : Dimensions: 26.8 cms x 29.7 cms x 4 cms Accuracy: The scale is designed for personal body weighing . Accuracy is guaranteed by the digit indicated below : 0 to 60 kg( 130 Lbs): +-1.2 digits >60-125 kg(271 Lbs): +-2.0 digits. Correct Usage: Stand gently & straight on the scale without leaning forward or backward. Adjustment to 0: To adjust dial to zero turn taring wheel given at the base of the scale. Cleaning: Use a soft cloth slightly moistened with mild detergent solution.
